OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRail fares in England to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frise by up to 4.9% in March
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Regulated train fares in England will  
OL,6, rise by up to 4.9% from March, the     
OL,7, Department for Transport has said.     
OL,9,FThe increase is capped below inflation 
OL,10,Fand will be delayed from January when  
OL,11,Fhikes usually come into force.         
OL,13,FIn the past, fares have risen based on 
OL,14,FJuly's retail price index (RPI) measure
OL,15,Fof inflation, plus an additional 1%.   
OL,17,FBut the Department for Transport has   
OL,18,Fdecided to limit fare price increases  
OL,19,Ffor a second year in a row below July's
OL,20,FRPI rate which was 9%.                 
